g.", "- Rutinen n\u00e5r noen kj\u00f8rer i feil kj\u00f8reretning er at tunnelen blir stengt med en gang, sier Sj\u00f8vold.", "Det er ogs\u00e5 mulig for trafikkoperat\u00f8rene \u00e5 sette ned hastigheten i tunnelen. I tillegg kan de sette p\u00e5 kj\u00f8refeltsignal over kj\u00f8refeltet til venstre, som viser at feltet er stengt.", "- P\u00e5 den m\u00e5ten kan vi pr\u00f8ve \u00e5 f\u00e5 trafikken over til h\u00f8yre kj\u00f8refelt, sier hun."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "1736959cdbe5b3e8fdbed64f3672e4a1ac03f1b1aa719e779e55d3667c1f4a48"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-01T14:30:10.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Fire ganger har bilister snudd i Strindheimtunnelen siden den ble \u00e5pnet."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article10056160.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/STRINDHEIMTUNNEL.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/be56ec5c4e9caae9e48660d69ddb74dee35b6c7f.jpg?597f3366"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["F\u00f8rst snur bilisten - s\u00e5 kj\u00f8rer vedkommende mot kj\u00f8reretningen -adressa.no", "Kunne g\u00e5tt verre", "- Uvitenhet", "Har flere virkemidler"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "be56ec5c4e9caae9e48660d69ddb74dee35b6c7f"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "automotive"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["bilist", "kj\u00f8reretning", "tunnelen", "kj\u00f8rt", "snur", "bilist snur", "feil kj\u00f8reretning"]}, {"field": 